</td></tr><tr valign="top"><td valign="top"><table border="0" width="95%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td class="classicdata">MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM <br /><img src="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/images/items/item_842.gif" height="40" width="40" align="right" alt="Cape of the Hatebringer" />Slot: BACK<br />AC: 6<br />STA: +5 DEX: +5 INT: +6 HP: +35 MANA: +35 <br />SV POISON +8 <br />Recommended level of 45<br />Effect: <a href="/spells/elemental-armor-id109.php" title="Elemental Armor">Elemental Armor</a> (Any Slot / Can Equip, Casting Time: 5.0 Seconds)<br />WT: 0.8 Size: MEDIUM<br />Class: <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/classes-wizard.php" title="Wizard">WIZ</a> <a href="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/classes-magician.php" title="Magician">MAG</a> <br />Race: ALL<br />Slot 1, Type 7: empty<br /></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><br /><hr width="95%" /><br /></div><div style="float: left; width: 50%;"><div class="itemimage" style="width: 50px; float:left;"><img src="http://www.everquest-online.com/content/images/items/item_842.gif" height="40" width="40" alt="Cape of the Hatebringer" /></div><div style="float: left; text-transform: uppercase;"><b>Magic Item</b><br /><b>Lore Item</b><br /></div><br style="clear: left" /><b>Item Type:</b> Armor<br /><b>Slots:</b> Back<br /><b>Weight:</b> 0.8&nbsp;<b>Size:</b> Medium<br /><br /><b>Armor Class:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">6</span><br /><b>Effect:</b> <a href="/spells/elemental-armor-id109.php" title="Elemental Armor">Elemental Armor</a> (Any Slot / Can Equip)<br /><b>Cast Time:</b> <span style="color: #FF0000;">5.0</span> Seconds<br /><br /><b>HP:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+35</span><br /><b>Mana:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+35</span><br /><b>Dexterity:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+5</span><br /><b>Intelligence:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+6</span><br /><b>Stamina:</b> <span style="color: #0000FF;">+5</span><br /><br /><b>Poison Resist:</b> <